Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.67,0:00:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier  而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.94,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.21,0:00:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.85,0:00:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕过危险的转角  追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.35,0:00:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.22,0:00:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.90,0:00:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.44,0:00:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.04,0:00:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.35,0:00:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.58,0:01:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.59,0:01:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.19,0:01:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.46,0:01:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.70,0:01:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.43,0:01:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻壳机动队 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞成这副模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无话可说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.63,0:01:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用实战培养新人的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把记忆换到电子脑里面行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野不会再生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像GHOST无法复制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算复制记忆  GHOST还是不会寄宿其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.29,0:02:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只考虑维持9课的运作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们或许不需要新的人才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是考虑今后的情势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.66,0:02:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们不得不克服的课题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.87,0:02:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这次作战还是不要安排阿东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好照顾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.11,0:02:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.29,0:02:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#20  北端的混迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.67,0:02:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的老朋友给的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.17,0:03:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认前俄军军官  现在改行做黑手党的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯·贾布罗夫和他的数名部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.44,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从该国运送钸元素进入择捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就是说久世那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.82,0:03:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去买那批钸元素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用核武器武装自己  宣布成为独立国家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大胆也要有个限度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧底侦查的谍报员被他的义体人同伴杀害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以致他们现在行踪不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谍报员被杀是2小时前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.38,0:03:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽然这么说  我们其实已经没有选择余地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.42,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们怎么特定地点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡乱跑去择捉也不会有结果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公安部给的情报里面似乎有提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说择捉市的佐川电子公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未经许可就扩建Berutarube区的地下工厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berutarube：位于择捉南端的旧型电脑都市，也是择捉的中心都市\N现在是多国企业与国际犯罪组织间利益关系复杂的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berutarube？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.44,0:04:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有俄国潜水艇基地的那个地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.88,0:04:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得俄军撤退的时候  已经炸毁埋起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.45,0:04:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐川的扩建工程如果顺利的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该已经挖到那个基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  真的很可疑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.66,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜水艇基地的话  拿来藏伪装船最合适
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没有确切证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设他们有在计划那么大的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.97,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当地的情报贩子应该也会掌握到什么才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.81,0:04:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长  我们就这样进入择捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一  请要求海上保安厅封锁出岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果难民拿到核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  所有的枷锁都会解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我相信你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候如果不能抓到久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内厅的行为就会消失在黑暗当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军方也将介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让出岛成为战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.87,0:05:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没有任何陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离交易还有一些时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们轮班休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要不要吃点这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真的很糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.28,0:05:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得跟课长抗议才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要检查一下电子脑活性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是对久世妄想的规模感到有点迷惑罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底有什么样的妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直截了当说的话  可以算是征服世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无药可救的夸大妄想狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你竟然会被那种东西迷惑\N一点都不像你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.44,0:06:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像思春期的小鬼\N遇到命中注定对象的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这样一切就清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然个别的11人病毒在他身上发作过一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.26,0:06:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他原本拥有的资质和思想产生了目前的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.73,0:06:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想本身确实很老套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我们不能一笑置之的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真心想要当上独裁者来促成世界和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.24,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且肾上腺素的分泌已经达到正常人会死亡的量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该认定久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经进入圣域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣域是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.46,0:07:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是已经变成傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.23,0:07:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从历史上来看  这种人可以发挥难以置信的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如"切·格瓦拉（古巴革命）"\N"麦康姆·X（黑人人权运动者）"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"卡西尔斯·克雷（拳王阿里）"就是这一类人的典型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟希特勒不同吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然某种意义上是同类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.07,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  思想上比较接近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是“甘地”和“金恩博士”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常跟他连线的难民们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借由装有划分和过滤装置的网络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.82,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉在他现场转播的行为当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他之所以不加上偏见也不打算共享意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他知道过了他的GHOST界线就是危险区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我那时也很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话一点都不有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川、帕兹、波玛待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备交易地点错误时的支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  军国主义者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危险的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经返还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  俄国人和日本人的摩擦不会马上就消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建设中的地下空洞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能穿过这里到达基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就能跟久世见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们有那个运气的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.11,0:09:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候只能跟佐川的工程人员直接面对面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.44,0:09:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没多余时间等少校的联络了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.69,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.19,0:10:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说要买武器  所以上了这艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  如果知道是你指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不必勉强在这里陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以就这样回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者消失在择捉的街头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会强迫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.45,0:10:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是最早教我们何谓革命的是“传说”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.62,0:10:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在出岛大部分的人都知道“久世同志”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.65,0:10:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是几乎没有人知道你的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不服气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.73,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到现在还是遵照“传说”的指导\N有自爆的觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种做法只是自我满足而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,革命是要有GHOST才会产生的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.41,0:10:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想知道你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给我能够相信你的根据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.74,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们要拿到手的武器是钸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.04,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用那个逼日本政府承认出岛是独立国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.85,0:11:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠的东西要确实还清\N这是最低限度的规则不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.06,0:11:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺威风的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么可以借给别人的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是大姐头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说克氯丹还在这里面做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是真的  请这边走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是非常谨慎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气  请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨  你在这里等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请这边走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也到这里就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.19,0:12:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界太殷勤会惹人厌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大姐头一起工作很辛苦对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不跟大姐头打好关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会后悔莫及的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克氯丹  是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.36,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根室登陆作战的时候  承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻性防壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才被烧死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入哪里被烧死的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.24,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  能烧死克氯丹这种程度的黑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术相当高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.44,0:13:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻性防壁的运作方式也是机密保持法所不允许的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.02,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁碟片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用这么旧的东西当外部记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.50,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那家伙花了那么多功夫  就为了删除这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐川的秘密帐簿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出货  柠檬蛋糕20公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柠檬蛋糕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每公斤50万美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M退出Au的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲介商  佐川K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B.J.\N柠檬蛋糕20公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.56,0:14:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K抽成40％＝退休金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买家\NB.P.介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所猜测的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.90,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在窃取钸的交易情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐川的K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.97,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K是北端特务课长加贺崎吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.21,0:14:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他担任仲介买卖每公斤50万美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖家是波利斯·贾布罗夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买家是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASIAN／B．P.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是指亚洲难民…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…刚刚的黑客是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加贺崎抽成的部分已经改成日元了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经把头款汇给佐川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2亿4千万日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难民从哪里拿到这么一大笔钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久世准备的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的话  他是怎么办到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.61,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  帮了我大忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.98,0:15:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还记得你说过佐川电子\N是你最讨厌的日系企业啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该辞掉报道厅的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.93,0:15:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  内厅说不定会是个比较好一点的机构
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.90,0:15:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川  交易地点在核潜艇基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个案子也有可能跟内厅有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.94,0:15:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.04,0:15:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.88,0:15:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在地底深处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯受到阻隔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上过去那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再告诉我一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.10,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说买钸至少要25万美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笔钱你要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从俄国人手上骗过来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我会老实付钱买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让国民理解我们的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱是我请一直消费难民的国民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点一点“捐”出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样说你大概听不懂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个设计是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.33,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在那些对自己的丰衣足食\N毫无自觉的国民总储蓄额
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很轻松就超过900兆日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.83,0:16:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实他们对这个数字也毫无自觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.37,0:16:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你知道这些储蓄的利息当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一笔表面上不存在的金额吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上不存在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一日元以下的金额
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终端机资料上通常也没有显示的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小数点以下的数字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要从网络上的帐户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征收这微薄几分钱的金额
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天就有数千万计的金额
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.23,0:17:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我设计程序把这些钱汇进我的银行户头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱就是从那里来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人根本不知道自己的帐户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.98,0:17:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小数点以下的存款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.42,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银行现在都把帐户管理交给AI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.15,0:17:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难民在这个国家工作明明就要预先扣税
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却完全不允许归化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民还是我行我素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.13,0:17:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没注意到系统做了多严重的压榨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.10,0:17:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只摄取着顺口又容易接受的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是一个欺瞒的社会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让大家知道这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那笔钱现在到底有多少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,107亿6千万吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的革命所能用的军事资金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一个恐怖分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有点醉心于英雄主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.87,0:18:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.21,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让船准备好随时可以出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是有问题的扩建区域吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该有得到许可吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.93,0:19:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是现场的负贵人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你刚刚说“又来了”对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前来了2台母公司的武装机甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.54,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再之前是一个俄国的奇怪义体人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.18,0:19:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提着两个大皮箱下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.98,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中奖了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么陆上自卫队也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有你一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.51,0:19:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾布罗夫与加贺崎都被公安盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一个人来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.65,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点完成交易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.63,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是指定帐户的汇款记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去确认吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们等一下马上过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.33,0:20:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此都一样无法确认内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下武器出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.34,0:21:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以违反兵器管制法和非法交易核物质的罪名逮捕你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我看你的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.58,0:22:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤  有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管这里  快去抓柯伊尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯伊尔·克拉斯诺夫：俄国战斗型义体人，钛制义手支架延伸至肩胛骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.22,0:22:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.99,0:22:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.92,0:22:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要确实破坏掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.83,0:22:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住  久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.60,0:22:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个放到地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不立刻开枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.28,0:22:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.22,0:22:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.08,0:22:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的猎物是你的人头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.62,0:22:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那恐怕很困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.79,0:22:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把皮箱拿到船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.06,0:22:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…\N快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.73,0:22:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧不起我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.25,0:23:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.95,0:23:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.53,0:23:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.50,0:23:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样美丽的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.83,0:23:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.37,0:23:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.44,0:23:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省视自身—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.25,0:23:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.35,0:23:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.72,0:23:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的—它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.73,0:24:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.86,0:24:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.04,0:24:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.70,0:24:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省视自身—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.71,0:24:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.95,0:24:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.45,0:24:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的—它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.35,0:24:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个躯壳里
